Package: teems
Title: Trade and Environment Equilibrium Modeling System
Description: Provides a reproducible workflow for Computable 
  General Equilibrium (CGE) model runs. Handles data loading and 
  aggregation, model file parsing, closure and shock 
  specification, and containerized model solution via Docker, 
  returning structured output for downstream analysis.
Version: 0.0.5
